The '''T'Chuk Sporting Arena''' was a shell-shaped stadium on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] that could hold 500,000 spectators and had a sand-covered field. It usually held [[Chin-bret/Legends|Chin-Bret]] games.

